  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201605/33c4fd48-189f-4fe8-8bb7-29f3d8a1fb46.jpg\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(16,113,181); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201605/33c4fd48-189f-4fe8-8bb7-29f3d8a1fb46.jpg\" style=\"height: 199px; width: 500px;\" /></a><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Writing: imagine a scenario or express your opinion</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Device</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: 28px; padding-right: 0px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A device is a think which is designed for a purpose. What is the device? How is it used? Who is using it?</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This week's topic: They bought a device... (90-110 words)</span><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Suggestions:</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">mobile device</span></span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2) literary device</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">3) connect the devices</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4) manage the devices</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tFor the first time in a very long time, Hodge was pleased with what he had. He had been so focused on getting what he wanted that he did not stop to enjoy the view. He believed he had to do whatever it took to reach his goal, but all of a sudden, he felt like he had kept his head in the sand for so long that he did not realize what was happening around him. His cell phone message rang for a second time. Reaching into his pocket, he took out the device to check the message.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167929726085/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799315/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799315\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.